## Stepper filter

Stepper filter is used to filter posts by a [Number field](docs.getvoxel.io_articles_number-field_.md)

## Options

- Label
- Placeholder
- Key
- Data source: Requires a Number field
- Range start
- Range end
- Step size
- Comparison:

1\. Equals selected value

2\. Greater than or equal to selected value

3\. Less than or equal to selected value
- Description
- Icon

This filer expects a number as a default value
